== CI WORKFLOW DETAILS ==

The .github/workflows/ci.yml defines:

**Triggers:** push to main, pull_request to main

**Job: rust (ubuntu-latest)**
- actions/checkout@v4
- dtolnay/rust-toolchain@stable with rustfmt, clippy components
- actions/cache@v4 for ~/.cargo/registry, ~/.cargo/git, target/ keyed by Cargo.lock hash
- cargo fmt --all -- --check
- cargo clippy --all-targets --all-features -- -D warnings
- cargo build --all-targets
- cargo test --all-targets

**Job: web (ubuntu-latest)**
- working-directory: web
- actions/checkout@v4
- actions/setup-node@v4 with node 20, npm cache
- npm ci
- npm run lint
- npm run typecheck
- npm run build
- npm run test

**Job: integration (ubuntu-latest, needs: rust)**
- PostgreSQL 16 service container (remote_harness user, test_password, remote_harness_test db)
- Health check: pg_isready
- DATABASE_URL env var set
- cargo test --test integration (with fallback if no integration tests found yet)

