== NOTES ==
- The npm cache had permission issues (root-owned files). Worked around by using npm_config_cache=/tmp/npm-cache for the install.
- Server integration tests (api_keys_test, chat_workflow_test, etc.) fail without a running PostgreSQL instance. This is expected and is why the CI has a separate integration job with a Postgres service container.
- The vitest/config import is used instead of vite's defineConfig because vitest v4 doesn't support the triple-slash reference types="vitest" directive that older versions used.
- buttonVariants export alongside Button component is standard shadcn/ui pattern; suppressed with eslint-disable comment.
